_json.gridTitle: Pull Wooden Fence Posts Set in Concrete WITH NO DIGGING!
_json.description: I wanted to post this to maybe help someone save a little time if they ever need to replace a fence, which has wooden posts that are set in concrete, and doesn't want to have to dig them out by hand.Here's the story.My very aging neighbor lady down the street asked me if I would replace about a ten foot section of her old cedar fence and update it to the same style her next door neighbor just put in. Of course I said yes. Now, truth be told, I am lazy, and work hard at it. I wanted to find a...
